thread.title: Reports of gunfire at Washington state college: police on scene

title: Reports of gunfire at Washington state college: police on scene
text:
Reports of gunfire at Washington state college: police on scene 6:15pm GMT - 00:30 
Highline College in Des Moines, Washington, ordered a lockdown of its campus on Friday morning as police responded to unconfirmed reports of gunfire, according to the college and the local police department. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
